description: Professional architectural blueprint for a 300 Acres house with We require a well-designed 3BHK floor plan for a residential unit within a large-scale development on 300 acres of land in Chennai, Tamil Nadu. The plan should include three spacious bedrooms, a living room, a kitchen with a dining area, and at least two bathrooms. One bedroom should ideally be a master with an attached bathroom. A balcony, utility space, and good ventilation are essential. The layout should maximize space efficiency while ensuring privacy and comfort. Consideration for natural lighting, Vaastu compliance (if possible), and sustainable materials is preferred. The design should stay within a budget of INR 200,000.. Top-down 2D floor plan with precise measurements, clean lines, labeled rooms, doors, windows, and dimensions. Technical architectural drawing style with blue lines on white background.
